        <text>
            <body>
                
                                        <p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324648" xml:id="d1e139545" corresp="Robert II de Châtillon, évêque de Langres (1203-1209)">Robertus, Dei gratia
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#317574" xml:id="d1e139547" corresp="Langres (Haute-Marne, Langres)">Lingonensis</placeName> episcopus</persName>, omnibus notum facio
                        presentibus pariter et futuris quod <persName key="d1e14261" xml:id="d1e139551">Ytericus, miles de <hi rend="italic">
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324430" xml:id="d1e139554" corresp="Champ-d'Oiseau (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Chaudesaul</placeName>
                            </hi>
                        </persName>, <lb n="2" /> et <persName key="d1e14267" xml:id="d1e139559">Oda</persName> uxor sua dederunt Deo et ecclesie beate Marie de
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e139562" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneto</orgName> in
                        perpetuam elemosinam pro animabus <lb n="3" /> suis et pro animabus
                        antecessorum suorum terram quam possidebant ad <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324983" xml:id="d1e139568" corresp="Pontem Thornodori">Pontem Thornodori</placeName>
                        citra viam et ultra <lb n="4" /> viam, et alteram portionem terre quam
                        habebant juxta grangiam <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325012" xml:id="d1e139573" corresp="Sancti Martini Melundenensis">Sancti Martini Melundenensis</placeName>, et pratum unum apud <lb n="5" />
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325023" xml:id="d1e139577" corresp="Saneveto">Sanevetum</placeName>
                        quod vulgo <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324333" xml:id="d1e139581" corresp="Nod-sur-Seine (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">
                            <foreign>Noam</foreign>
                        </placeName> vocant, quod partiuntur per medium cum <persName key="d1e14273" xml:id="d1e139585">Johanne, milite de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325023" xml:id="d1e139587" corresp="Saneveto">Saneveto</placeName>
                        </persName>, et nepotibus <lb n="6" /> suis, et est totum de prefate
                            <persName key="d1e14279" xml:id="d1e139592">Ode</persName> hereditate.
                        Quam videlicet elemosinam supradictus <persName key="d1e14286" xml:id="d1e139595">Ytericus</persName> et <lb n="7" />
                        <persName key="d1e14292" xml:id="d1e139600">Oda</persName> uxor sua
                        memoratis fratribus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e139603" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonten<supplied>etensibus</supplied>
                        </orgName>, cum heredibus ipsius <persName key="d1e14298" xml:id="d1e139608">Yterici</persName> et <persName key="d1e14304" xml:id="d1e139611">Ode</persName> legitime garantire <sic>greent<lb n="8" break="no" />verunt</sic>. Hoc totum laudaverunt liberi ipsorum : <persName key="d1e14310" xml:id="d1e139619">Agnella</persName> scilicet, <persName key="d1e14316" xml:id="d1e139623">Pontius</persName> et <persName key="d1e14323" xml:id="d1e139626">Ytericus</persName>. Hoc etiam
                        similiter lau<lb n="9" break="no" />davit <persName key="d1e14329" xml:id="d1e139631">Bartholomeus <addName>Ad Pollices</addName>
                        </persName> de cujus casamento cotura erat. Quod ut ratum habeatur, in
                            pos<lb n="10" break="no" />terum presentem paginam sigilli mei munimine
                        roboravi. Actum anno gratie .M°. <figure />CC°. <figure />V°.</p>
                
            </body>
